"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.18\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.18</span> 标题：容器、器皿（containers, vessels）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אָסוּךְ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’asuk)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:2\">2KI 4:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּקְבֻּק</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：baqbuq)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:3\">1KI 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:1\">JER 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:10\">JER 19:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֶרֶשׂ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：cheres)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23\">PRO 26:23</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כְּלִי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kli)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:25\">GEN 42:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:11\">GEN 43:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:20\">GEN 45:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:16\">EXO 37:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:21\">LEV 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:21\">LEV 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:32\">LEV 11:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:33\">LEV 11:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:34\">LEV 11:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:5\">LEV 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:50\">LEV 14:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:12\">LEV 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:12\">LEV 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:9\">NUM 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:17\">NUM 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:15\">NUM 19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:17\">NUM 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:25\">DEU 23:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:9\">RUT 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:7\">1SA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:28\">2SA 17:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:10\">1KI 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3\">2KI 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3\">2KI 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:4\">2KI 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:6\">2KI 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:6\">2KI 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:6\">2KI 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:7\">EST 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:7\">EST 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:7\">EST 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:17\">JOB 28:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:9\">PSA 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:24\">ISA 22:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:24\">ISA 22:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:24\">ISA 22:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:4\">ISA 65:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:20\">ISA 66:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:3\">JER 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:4\">JER 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:4\">JER 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:11\">JER 19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:28\">JER 22:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:14\">JER 32:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer40:10\">JER 40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:11\">JER 48:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:11\">JER 48:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:12\">JER 48:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:38\">JER 48:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:34\">JER 51:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:9\">EZK 4:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֶצֶב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘etsev)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:28\">JER 22:28</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἀγγεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：aggeion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:4\">MAT 25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt7:20\">JDT 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:5\">JDT 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir21:14\">SIR 21:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:53\">1MA 6:53</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἄγγος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：aggos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:48\">MAT 13:48</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἄντλημα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：antlēma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:11\">JHN 4:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κάλπη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kalpē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc3:12\">4MA 3:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：καψάκης</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kapsakēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:5\">JDT 10:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σκεῦος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：skeuos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:16\">LUK 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:21\">ROM 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:27\">REV 2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:15\">LJE 1:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉：vas</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd6:56\">2ES 6:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd9:34\">2ES 9:34</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0052_storage_containers.png\" alt=\"OAI-0052_storage_containers\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>容器是用来装东西的坚固物品。容器有陶制的、金属制的，也有木制的，大小和形状差别很大。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0490_flask.jpg\" alt=\"瓶\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">瓶 (Metropolitan Museum of Art, CC0, MMA)</figcaption></figure>大多数语言都有表示容器的统称。希伯来文<em>kli</em> 一词的含义非常笼统，用法与英文“implement”（“用具”）、“instrument”（“工具”）、甚至是“object”（“物体”）或“thing”（“东西”）类似。翻译者应根据语境选择相应的译词。例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:9\">RUT 2:9</a> 中，该词明显是指人们用来喝水的容器，翻译者可能要指出这一点；例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 译为“water jars”（“水罐”），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 译为“water jugs”（“水壶”）。在大多数经文中，翻译者都可以选择一个一般性词语，但应避免译作由塑料、橡胶、锡或其他圣经时期没有的材料制成的容器。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:2\">2KI 4:2</a> 中，希伯来文<em>’asuk</em> 指的是某种罐子或长颈瓶，可能是陶制的。大多数译本都在译词前面添加了修饰词“小”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>baqbuq</em> 一词指的是一种细颈小瓶。在现代希伯来文中，这个词表示“瓶子”。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23\">PRO 26:23</a> 中，希伯来文<em>cheres</em> 指的是一种由廉价而普通的材料制成的器皿。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:17\">JOB 28:17</a> ：这节经文末尾的希伯来文字面意思是“精金的器皿”。虽然大多数译本都采取了“精金的珠宝”（“jewels of fine gold”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）等类译法，但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 和其他译本认为“器皿”（希伯来文<em>kli</em> ）指的是“金瓶子”，这可能比“珠宝”更准确。在一些语言中，“精金的器皿”可以译为“用精金做的罐子”。因为经文的要旨是智慧极其可贵，而不是把它与任何物品作比较；翻译者可以借鉴<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 来翻译整节经文，“没有任何东西与它等价——不论是金子还是贵重的玻璃。”</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:4\">MAT 25:4</a> 中提到的器皿应该比较小，容量不超过1升（约1夸脱）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:48\">MAT 13:48</a> 提到的容器应该很大，容量可能有15—19升（4—5加仑）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:11\">JHN 4:11</a> ：撒玛利亚妇人看见耶稣“没有打水的器具”。希腊文<em>antlēma</em> （<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:11\">JHN 4:11</a> ）源自一个意为“打水”的动词，并没有提示器具的形状和材料。许多译本译为“桶”。但是，这种译法可能会暗示这是一种用金属、塑料甚或橡胶做的器具，而这些都是不合适的。即便是木桶，也不太可能出现在新约时期。这里比较可能是一个皮制的容器。在许多语言中，最好的解决办法是不指明具体的器具。翻译者可以用妇女的话来开始该节经文：“先生，井很深，但你没有打水的东西。”<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 、PV 和其他一些译本采用了类似的译法。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a> ：<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 将希腊文<em>skeuos</em> 一词译为“bowl”（“碗”），还有译本译为“jar”（“罐子”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ）。这里最好使用一个统称，如“器皿”或“容器”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> ）。<em>skeuos</em> 一词在新约中通常是指广义的“东西、物件、物品”（参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:29\">MAT 12:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:27\">MRK 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:16\">MRK 11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:31\">LUK 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:11\">ACT 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:16\">ACT 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:5\">ACT 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:17\">ACT 27:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:20\">2TI 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:21\">2TI 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:21\">HEB 9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:12\">REV 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:12\">REV 18:12</a> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
